    {
      "id": 2456,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "Uber has a feature in the iOS app to apply a promotion code right after we register an account.\n\nSince there was no protection against brute force attacks, we were able to enumerate promotion codes, like in report #125505.\n\nThis is a similar bug but leaks more information than #125505:\n\n* Promo code value\n* Country\n* Inviter’s name\n* Inviter’s picture\n\n\n\n",
